# Go to volkanpay login page
* Go to "https://www.volkanpay.com/login"
## NonCampaign Bank Transfer Verification
* Write "user_name" to input "username_input"
* Write "password" to input "password_input"
* Click the "login_button" button
* Check "https://www.volkanpay.com/home" URL
* Click the "menu_transfer" button
* Check "https://www.volkanpay.com/transfer" URL
* Input "balance_input" writes "100"
* Click the "non_campaign_bank_selector" button
* Write "100" to input "transfer_amount_input"
* Write "Fatih Saltok" to input "recipient_name_input"
* Click the "complete_transfer_button" button
* Wait "3" second
* Input "balance_input" writes "0"